<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Banking Question</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Holly Golightly">Holly Golightly</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 1:32 p.m. 23/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Banking Question<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>If I decided to make the trip to Neriak and get bound there, but first put all my valuables in the Oggok Bank, would I be able to get them out of the Neriak Bank? Is banking in EQ like UO (i.e. universal) or are banks autonomous?

<P>I hope banks are universal...otherwise what a pain in the ass. I get killed around Neriak and someone loots my weapon and all my coins...if I have another weapon in the bank, how am I to retrieve it (make the trip back to Oggok?) or even get any coins to buy a new one (make the trip back to Oggok?)?
<P>If banking isn't Universal, what will motivate me to ever go more then 2 zones from Oggok
<P>Holly.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
